  Lun7 kau3 sia2-ji7 iah8 si7 an2-ni, tui3 an2-ni khoaN3, peh8-oe7-ji7 sit8-chai7 u7 toa7 li7-ek, lan2 kiam2 m7-tioh8 tui3-tiong7 liu5-sim lai5-oh8 mah ? 
  [Cheng5 te7-it, te7-ji7, te7-saN tiuN e5 Kau3-hoe7-po3, u7 in3 Iap8 Bok8-su sou2-cho3 lun7 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 li7-ek. TaN chiong Lau5 Bou7-chheng te7-ji7-mia5 e5 lun7 in3 ti7 chia hou7 lin2 thak8 . I sou2 cho3-e5 khah-te2, sou2-i2 thang cho3-chit8-e7 in3 . ] 
  ThiN-e7 tak8-kok e5 ji7 bo5 long2 siang7-khoan2; tau3-ti2 long2 u7 lou7-eng7; taN che3 peh8-oe7-ji7 ia7 si7 bun5-ji7-tiong e5 chit8-lui7, i-e5 li7-ek lang5, pi2 pat8-ho7 e5 ji7, iau2 u7 khah-kin2 khah-khoai3 . TaN chiong i-e5 lou7-eng7 tai7-liok8 lai5 kong2 ti7 e7-te2 . 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 pang-chan7 kau3-hoe7 heng-ong7, tu2-tioh8 khun2-tiok8 be7 hoe3-bo5 . Kau3-hoe7 sou2-i2 bo5 heng-ong7, in-ui7 jip8-kau3 e5 lang5 bo5 chhim-chai to7-li2; bo5 chhim-chai to7-li2, in-ui7 ka-ti7 be7-hiau2 thak8 Seng3-keng; be7-hiau2 thak8 Seng3-keng, in-ui7 m7-bat ji7 . Khong2-chu2-ji7 oh ke2-soeh, na7 bat bo5 chhim, iu5-goan5 khoaN3 be7-lai5; kan-ta thiaN Sian-siN kong2, chiu7 sou2 bat--e5 iu2-han7, bo5 thiaN-tioh8--e5 chiu7 m7-chai; thiaN ku2--e5 iu7 be7 ki3-tit, ho5-hong3 u7 si5 hou7-lai5 chui2-chhim chou2-tong3; se3-su7 kiau2-jiau2, peN7-thiaN3 chou2-gai7, be7-e7 tak8 le2-pai3 long2 kau3 le2-pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2 ? ThiaN to7-li2 e5 lang5 na7 kheng2 khin5 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7, chiu7 chit8-ni5-ku2 put-lun7 lam5-hu7 lo2-iu3 long2 e7 ka-ti7 thak8 Seng3-keng, khah chai to7-li2; m7-bian2 theng3-hau7 kau3 pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2, ti7 ke-lai7 cha2-am3 ia7 thang thak8, tit-tioh8 li7-ek. Koh u7-si5 tu2-tioh8 chou2-tong3 be7 tang3 kau3 pai3-tng5 siu7 ka3-si7, chiu7 thang ka-ti7 khoaN3 chhian2-beng5 to7-li2 e5 chheh, iuN2-chhi7 sim-sin5, ia7 e7 li7-ek thiaN e5 lang5. Kau3-hoe7 e5 lang5 na7 bo5 khoaN3-khin peh8-oe7-ji7, tek-khak e7 na2-ku2 na2-toa7 chin3-pou7. Koh thiaN-kiN3 A-hui-li7-ka e5 tang-peng5 u7 chit8-e5 hai2-su7, mia5 Ma2-tat8-ka-su-ka, ti7 hia kau3-hoe7 tu2-tioh8 khun2-tiok8, ji7-gou7-ni5-ku2 bo5 Bok8-su ti7-teh ; kau3 khun2-tiok8 soah, Bok8-su koh khi3, khoaN3-kiN3 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 pi2-cheng5 koh khah-che7; chiu7-si7 in-ui7 u7 pun2-te7 e5 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 Seng3-chheh ti7-teh, lang5 e7 hiau2 ka-ti7 thak8. Che thang pin5-ki3 kau3-hoe7 e5 lang5 m7-thang bo5 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 . 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 lu2-jin5 u7 ti3-hui7 . Hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 chai5-tiau7 bo5 khah-su ta-pou-lang5, sou2-i2 e7 bo5 hak8-bun7, in-ui7 Khong2-chu2-ji7 oh-thak8 . Na7 boeh thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7, tui3 lak8-hoe3 kau3 chap8-hoe3 si3-ni5 e5 ku2, chiu7 bo5 be7-hiau2-sia2 e5 ji7, iah8 bo5 be7-hiau2-thak8 e5 chheh ; an2-ni kiam2 m7-si7 chin toa7 e5 lou7-eng7?
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 tak8-teng2 cho3-kang e5 lang5 e7 hiau2 thak8 Seng3-chheh, kap chai che7-che7 hang7 e5 tai7-chi3. Tak8-teng2 cho3-kang e5 lang5 tak8-jit8 u7 kang tiN5-poaN3, iau2-ku2 na7 boeh thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 un2-tang3 e7 khi2-lai5. Goa2 khoaN3 hian7-si5 teh thiaN to7-li2--e5 khah-che7 si7 choh-sit kap chau2-than3 e5 lang5, pun2 m7-bat poaN3-ji7; tui3 thiaN to7-li2 chiaN3 tak8-pai2 An-hioh-jit8 oh8 thak8 ji7-bo2, tng tu2-a2 teh-thak8 e5 si5 m7-kaN2 siuN7 e7 bat, na7-si7 kau3-boe2 long2 e7 ka-ti7 thak8, m7-bian2 tiaN7-tiaN7 oa2-kho3 pat8-lang5 lai5 ka3 . Chiong-lai5 peh8-oe7-ji7 na2 che7 lang5 bat, chiu7 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 chheh ia7 e7 na2-chhut na2-che7 iuN7, kiam2-chhai2 Thian-bun5 Te7-li2 e5 chheh ; a2-si7 Soan3-hak8 Kek-but8 e5 chheh; Lek8-tai7 e5 tai7-chi3,tak8-kok e5 sin-bun5; che long2 e7 ke-thiN lang5 e5 ti3-hui7; an2-ni2-siN kiam2 thang kong2 peh8-oe7-ji7 m7-bian2 thak8 e7 cho3-tit ? 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 lang5 khah-khoai3 bat Khong2-chu2-ji7. Na7 seng thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 kau3 e7 sia2, ti7 thak8 Khong2-chu2-ji7 e5 si5 hoan7 u7 m7-bat e5 ji7, kap be7-hiau2 ke2-soeh e5 i3-gi7; na7-sai2 mng7 sian-siN chit8-pai2, eng7 peh8-oe7-ji7 chu3 -beng5, chiu7 e7 ka-ti7 thak8, m7-bian2 kiaN koh be7 ki3-tit; an2-ni si7 thak8 Khong2-chu2-ji7, ia7 tioh8 kiam eng7 peh8-oe7-ji7 . peh8-oe7-ji7 oe7 hou7 m7 bat thak8 Khong2-chu2-ji7 e5 lang5 bat Khong2-chu2-ji7. Goa2 sou2 bat e5 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5, lai7-tiong u7 nng7 lang5 chu7 soe3 bo5 thak8-chheh, kau3 ji7-chap8 chhut-thau5 he3 chiah thiaN to7-li2, oh8-thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7; hian7-si5 lian5 Tng5-lang5-ji7 e5 Seng3-chheh, kap sin-bun5 ia7 khoaN3 oe7 lai5: na7 m7 si7 bat peh8-oe7-ji7 thai3-tho2 u7 thang an2-ni?
