  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 san3-hiong-lang5 e5 chu2-te7 u7 ti3-hui7. San3-hiong-lang5 e5 chu2-te7 chai5-cheng5 be7 long2 khah-su ho2-giah8-lang5 e5 chu2-te7 ; kho2-sioh se3-han3 e5 si5 i bo5 thak8-chheh ; a2-si7 thak8 bo5 kui2-ni5 koh khi3 cho3-kang, kau3-boe2 u7 thak8 na2 bo5 thak8, iu5-goan5 m7-bat ji7. Peh8-oe7-ji7 na7 thak8 kau3 e7 sia2, chiu7 m7-bian2-kiaN e7 hui3-bo5-khi3, in-ui7 u7 ji7-bo2 thang chhiat-im, chit8-e7 hou, ji7 chiu7 ti7-teh ; khoaN3 beh kong2 sim2-mih8 oe7, siuN7 lai5 tau3 chiu7 u7 ji7, m7-bian2 chhin-chhiuN7 Khong2-chu2-ji7 u7 thak8-tioh8--e5 chiaN3 bat, bo5 thak8-tioh8--e5 chiu7 m7-bat . Koh tioh8 u7 thak8 koe3, chiaN3 chai hit-e5 kou3-tian2, bo5 thak8-koe3, chiu7 m7-chai hit-e5 in-iu5. Koh lang5 na7 beh bat Khong2-chu2-ji7 kau3 khoaN3 e7 lai5, sia2 e7 khi3, tioh8 tui3 se3-han3 tit8-tit8 thak8 kau3 chiaN5-chap8-ni5-ku2 chiaN3-e7, ia7 u7 kau3 chiaN5 chap8-ni5-ku2, kah i thak8 pun lang5 thiaN, kong2 be7 tit-lai5; u7 tai7-chi3 kah i ki3, sia2 be7 tit lai5. Peh8-oe7-ji7 m7-bian2 thak8 hiah-che7-ni5: m7-bian2 tui3 se3-han3 thak8 na7 kau3 bat, beh-thak8 beh-sia2 bo5 m7 sui5 -i3 . Kau3-hoe7-tiong e5 lang5 chiah8 kau3 saN-chap8-goa7-hoe3, si3-chap8-goa7-hoe3, gou7-chap8-hoe3 chiah oh8-thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 lang5 put-chi2 che7, koah-si7 kau3 sek8-sek8 e7 thak8 hou7 pat8-lang5 thiaN. U7 che3 peh8-oe7-ji7, san3-hiong lang5 e5 chu2-te7 m7-bian2 khou2 m7-bat ji7 . 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 bo5 siu7 kau3-hoa3 e5 lang5 piN3-cho3 u7 hak8-bun7; ku7-te2 bo5-ji7 piN3-kau3 u7 ji7. Cha2-jit8 lam5-iuN5 che7-che7 hai2-su7 bo5 siu7 kau3-hoa3; m7-bat le2-gi5, sim7-chi3 thai5-si2 lang5 soa3 chiah8-bah. Tui3 u7 Bok8-su khi3 thoan5 to7-li2, hak8-sip8 i-e5 thou2-im chhong3 peh8-oe7-ji7 ; tui3 an2-ni hong-siok8 toa7 pian3-oaN7, lang5 chiam7-chiam7 u7 ti3-hui7, kok-tou7 na2 -ku2 na2-heng ; kau3-hoe7 lang5-giah8 chit8-ni5 chit8-ni5 ke. M7-si7 peh8-oe7-ji7, thai3-tho2 e7 hou7 bo5 ji7 e5 sou2-chai7 piN3-cho3 u7 ji7, pian3-oaN7 kau3 hiah-kin2 ? Lan2 e5 Hong5-te3 chai soaN--nih8 e5 chhiN-hoan m7-bat le2-gi5, tiau5-ti5 siat gi7-oh8 chhiaN2 sian-siN lai5 ka3, tui3 siat kau3-taN chiong-kin7 peh-ni5-ku2; chha-put-to bo5 chit8-e5 bat-ji7 . In-ui7 ji7 kap oe7 bo5 siang7, tai7-seng kan-ta thak8 ji7-im long2 be7-hiau2 sim2-mih8 i3-su3, thak8-liau2 tioh8 koh ke2-soeh. Hiah-e5 chhiN-hoan e5 gin2-na2 kan-ta thiaN Sian-siN kong2, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ah-a2 thiaN lui5, thiaN chit8-e5 siaN tiaN7-tiaN7. Phi3-ju7 na7 chiong peh8-oe7-ji7 hoan-ek8 in e5 im, thak8 in e5 oe7, tek-khak khah u7 eng3-hau7 .
  Goa2 chiau3 goa2 gu5-gong7 e5 i3-kian3, chiong peh8-oe7-ji7 kap Khong2-chu2-ji7 saN-pi2 lai5-lun7, m7-si7 hiam5 Khong2-chu2-ji7 bo5 lou7-eng7; put-ko3 kong2 peh8-oe7-ji7 khah khoai3 bat, hou7 lang5 khah-kin2 chin3-pou7 ; m7-bian2 kau3 ku2-ku2 tiaN7-tiaN7 hou7 ji7 pak8-teh . Iu7 koh hap8 ti7 lam5-hu7 lo2-iu3, pin5-chian7 hu3-kui3 tak8-teng2 e5 lang5 long2 thak8 e7 khi2. An2-ni kiam2 m7-si7 put-chi2 toa7 lou7-eng7? 
